    "Setting .frame(maxWidth: .infinity) makes views expand equally within their container, ensuring consistent sizing across items" : {
      "comment" : "A description of how to ensure that views within a container are sized consistently.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Das Setzen von .frame(maxWidth: .infinity) lässt Ansichten innerhalb ihres Containers gleichmäßig wachsen und sorgt für konsistente Größen zwischen Elementen"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Définir .frame(maxWidth: .infinity) fait s’étendre les vues de manière égale dans leur conteneur, assurant des tailles cohérentes entre les éléments"
          }
        },
        "hi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : ".frame(maxWidth: .infinity) set करने से views अपने container में बराबर expand होते हैं, जिससे items में consistent sizing बनी रहती है"
          }
        },
        "nl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Door .frame(maxWidth: .infinity) in te stellen, worden weergaven even groot binnen hun container, zodat items consistent worden uitgelijnd"
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Если задать .frame(maxWidth: .infinity), представления будут равномерно растягиваться внутри контейнера, обеспечивая одинаковый размер элементов"
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : ".frame(maxWidth: .infinity) ayarlamak, view’ların container içinde eşit genişlemesini sağlar ve items arasında consistent sizing sunar"
          }
        },
        "uk" : {
